OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA sunny start to the day, but
OL,6,Fskies turning hazy, leading to bright
OL,7,Fspells during the afternoon.
OL,8,FTemperatures close to the late June
OL,9,Faverage.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FLargely dry with sunny spells next
OL,13,Fweek, but a few showers possible at
OL,14,Ftimes, particularly on Tuesday. Light
OL,15,Fwinds. Feeling pleasant in the
OL,16,Fsunshine with near normal temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
